snippet.title: Arcade Longplay - Bosconian (1981) Namco
snippet.description: Full playthrough of the popular space-shooter game with parallax scrolling Bosconian. Released back in 1981, the game features speech, quality graphics, fast action gameplay and excellent sounds.
